  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Sketch Lab: Brand Kit ",
    "long_instructions": "##Build a Mini Brand Kit\r\n- Select a fictional product represented within Sketch Lab. \r\n- Select a sample user persona\r\n- Build a **mini brand kit** with:\r\n    - 3–5 color swatches\r\n    - A font pair (heading + body text)\r\n    - 1–2 descriptive style words (e.g., sleek, bold, approachable)\r\n- Connect your design choices for your fictional product back to the sample user persona.",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Design a mini brand kit for a fictional product that reflects the needs of a chosen user persona.",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://images.code.org/9ec2319247c597ffcc1f04ecbd019f2d-graphic-designer.png",
