            "fontSize": 20,
            "fontFamily": 3,
            "text": "User Persona #3\n\nWho he is: Juggles class, \nwork, and family errands. \nBilingual \n(Spanish/English).\n\nHabits & prefs: Uses school\nChromebook + budget \nAndroid; watches how-to \nclips.\n\nNeeds: Step-by-step flows, \nbilingual support, works-\non-anything reliability.\n",
