            "fontSize": 20,
            "fontFamily": 3,
            "text": "User Persona #4\n\nWho she is: Club officer, \ngroup-chat admin, event \nplanner in sneakers.\n\nHabits & prefs: Makes \nshared docs; loves \ntemplates; posts recaps, \nnot selfies.\n\nNeeds: Easy ways to \ncoordinate, share, and \ncelebrate together.\n",
            "textAlign": "center",
            "verticalAlign": "top",
            "containerId": "q1eJtc9XsNJCxfkP76c6L",
            "originalText": "User Persona #4\n\nWho she is: Club officer, group-chat admin, event planner in sneakers.\n\nHabits & prefs: Makes shared docs; loves templates; posts recaps, not selfies.\n\nNeeds: Easy ways to coordinate, share, and celebrate together.\n",
