            "updated": 1760476685091,
            "link": null,
            "locked": false,
            "fontSize": 20,
            "fontFamily": 3,
            "text": "I picked soft blue and mint as calm “coordination” colors, with a warm apricot accent \nthat feels like an invite. Black is the anchor for high-contrast schedules and codes \nshe’ll share. The rounded display heading reads like a friendly flyer; the clean sans \nbody keeps checklists and instructions easy to scan. Our style words—conscience and \nthoughtful—signal Patch & Play’s eco values and Sophie’s care for her club. Copy uses \n“we” language and clear next steps, so it’s simple to plan and celebrate together. \nNothing shouts; everything guides.",
            "textAlign": "left",
            "verticalAlign": "top",
            "containerId": "zcrEmjTn4QO32JAHINil3",
            "originalText": "I picked soft blue and mint as calm “coordination” colors, with a warm apricot accent that feels like an invite. Black is the anchor for high-contrast schedules and codes she’ll share. The rounded display heading reads like a friendly flyer; the clean sans body keeps checklists and instructions easy to scan. Our style words—conscience and thoughtful—signal Patch & Play’s eco values and Sophie’s care for her club. Copy uses “we” language and clear next steps, so it’s simple to plan and celebrate together. Nothing shouts; everything guides.",
            "lineHeight": 1.2,
            "baseline": 163
          },
