            "fontSize": 20,
            "fontFamily": 3,
            "text": "User Persona #1\n\nWho she is: Varsity winger \n+ part-time barista. Ten-\nminute passing periods are \nher whole window.\n\nHabits & prefs: Saves \nfavorite orders; lactose-\nsensitive; lives in Notes \nand Reminders; cracked \niPhone screen.\n\nNeeds: Speed, price \nclarity, and simple choices\nthat don’t derail her day.\n\n",
            "textAlign": "center",
            "verticalAlign": "top",
            "containerId": "G_4nfsucfxkiGC9zFDOTf",
            "originalText": "User Persona #1\n\nWho she is: Varsity winger + part-time barista. Ten-minute passing periods are her whole window.\n\nHabits & prefs: Saves favorite orders; lactose-sensitive; lives in Notes and Reminders; cracked iPhone screen.\n\nNeeds: Speed, price clarity, and simple choices that don’t derail her day.\n\n",
