            "fontSize": 20,
            "fontFamily": 3,
            "text": "User Persona #2\n\nWho he is: Practices late, \nstudies later. Earbuds \nalways in, notifications \nmostly off.\n\nHabits & prefs: Dark mode, \nhaptics off, hates sudden \nsounds; likes quiet status \ncues.\n\nNeeds: Low-glare UI, gentle\nfeedback, and control over \nalerts.\n",
            "textAlign": "center",
            "verticalAlign": "top",
            "containerId": "aRCW3ZKuWSnhugydumI7k",
            "originalText": "User Persona #2\n\nWho he is: Practices late, studies later. Earbuds always in, notifications mostly off.\n\nHabits & prefs: Dark mode, haptics off, hates sudden sounds; likes quiet status cues.\n\nNeeds: Low-glare UI, gentle feedback, and control over alerts.\n",
